                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7558" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1186</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3158 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“与收益相关”还是“与资产相关”？——希努尔的政府补助分类之困</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Income-Related&quot; or &quot;Asset-Related&quot;? -- Sinoer&#39;s Dilemma of Government Grants Classification</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许楠，王婧茜，李君妍，朱清香</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">希努尔男装股份有限公司（现已更名为雪松发展股份有限公司）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">政府补助分类；与收益相关；与资产相关；希努尔;2023百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Government grants classification; Income-related; Asset-related; Sinoer</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017年财政部修订印发了政府补助准则，一些上市公司由于未能准确理解准则内容，在实务工作中出现了政府补助会计处理的错误，违背了可靠性的会计信息质量要求，对经济市场的规范运行产生了负面影响。本案例聚焦希努尔2018年收到的多笔政府补助（旅游产业发展奖励资金），以企业内部讨论后决定将其分类为与收益相关的政府补助为起点，描述其当时虽没有被深交所继续问询，但后续却被证监会责令更正为与资产相关的政府补助的全过程。通过复现希努尔多笔政府补助曲折的分类认定过程，采用“AB双案例”模式创设问题情境，递进式引导学生自主判断政府补助的类型；提升学生的会计职业判断能力与思辨能力，使其深刻领悟政府补助准则的背后逻辑，让学生在知其然的基础上，知其所以然。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2017, the Ministry of Finance revised and issued the government grant standards. Due to the failure to accurately understand the standards, some listed companies made mistakes in the accounting treatment of government subsidies in their practical work, which violated the quality requirements of reliable accounting information and played a negative role in the standardized operation of the economic market. This case focuses on the multiple government subsidies (tourism industry development incentive funds) that Sinoer received in 2018. Starting from the internal discussion of the enterprise, it decided to classify them as revenue-related government subsidies, and describes the whole process of the company being ordered to be corrected into asset-related government subsidies by the CSRC although it was not further investigated by the Shenzhen Stock Exchange at that time. By reproducing the tortuous classification and identification process of Sinoer&#39;s multiple government subsidies, the &quot;AB double cases&quot; model is adopted to create a problem situation and progressively guide students to judge the types of government subsidies independently. Improve the students&#39; professional judgment and critical thinking ability of accounting, so that they can deeply understand the logic behind the government subsidy criteria, so that students can know the why on the basis of knowing the why.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》《会计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">政府补助分类；政府补助会计处理；会计信息质量要求（可靠性）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
